-# Houston Sip Queen Theme
-
-A luxury mobile bartending WordPress theme for Houston Sip Queen - Southern glam, nightlife elegance, and premium cocktail experiences.
-
-## Features
-
-- **Luxury Southern Glam Design**: Onyx, Champagne, RoseGold, and Berry color palette with elegant typography
-- **Mobile Bartending Focus**: Cocktail galleries, package showcases, and event booking forms
-- **Interactive Animations**: Champagne bubbles, floating cocktail glasses, and sparkle effects
-- **Custom Post Types**: Events and Cocktails with detailed meta fields
-- **Quote Form Integration**: Professional inquiry forms with validation
-- **Responsive Design**: Mobile-first approach optimized for all devices
-- **SEO Optimized**: Built-in SEO best practices for local business marketing
-
-## Installation
-
-1. Download the theme ZIP file
-2. Upload to WordPress admin under Appearance > Themes > Add New > Upload Theme
-3. Activate the "Houston Sip Queen" theme
-4. Configure theme options in Customizer
-5. Set up Event and Cocktail post types
-6. Configure contact information and service areas
-
-## Theme Structure
-
-```
-houstonsipqueen-theme/
-├── style.css              # Main stylesheet with luxury brand styling
-├── functions.php          # Theme functions and custom post types
-├── index.php              # Main blog template
-├── front-page.php         # Front page with hero and service sections
-├── header.php             # Header with luxury navigation
-├── footer.php             # Footer with champagne animations
-├── template-parts/        # Reusable template parts
-│   └── hero-luxury.php    # Luxury mobile bartending hero section
-├── js/                    # JavaScript files
-│   └── script.js          # Theme interactions and animations
-├── images/                # Theme images and assets
-├── screenshot.png         # Theme preview image
-└── README.md              # This file
-```
-
-## Brand Colors & Typography
-
-### Color Palette
-- **Onyx**: `#0B0B0F` (primary text, headers)
-- **Champagne**: `#F5E6C8` (accents, backgrounds)
-- **RoseGold**: `#C9A26A` (buttons, highlights)
-- **Berry**: `#7A1E3A` (secondary accents)
-- **White**: `#FFFFFF` (backgrounds)
-
-### Typography
-- **Headings**: Playfair Display / Cinzel (serif)
-- **Body**: Inter / Montserrat (sans-serif)
-- **Accent**: Script fonts for special elements
-
-## Custom Post Types
-
-### Events
-- **Fields**: Event Date, Time, Location, Guest Count, Package Selected
-- **Features**: Event management, booking integration
-- **Display**: Calendar views, event grids, booking forms
-
-### Cocktails
-- **Fields**: Primary Spirit, Sweetness Level, Complexity Level
-- **Features**: Recipe management, filtering by preferences
-- **Display**: Cocktail galleries, featured drinks, menus
-
-## Customization
-
-### Theme Customizer Options
-- **Business Phone**: Contact number display
-- **Service Area**: Geographic service information
-- **Hero Gradient**: Background color customization
-
-### Page Templates
-- **Front Page**: Hero + Services + Packages + Quote Form
-- **Blog**: Standard blog layout with luxury styling
-- **Events**: Event listings and booking pages
-- **Cocktails**: Drink menus and recipe pages
-
-## Package Features
-
-### Signature Experience ($1,500)
-- Professional mobile bar setup
-- 8 signature cocktails
-- Premium glassware & garnishes
-- 3 hours of service
-- Up to 50 guests
-
-### Premium Package ($2,200)
-- Everything in Signature
-- Custom cocktail menu
-- Non-alcoholic options
-- 4 hours of service
-- Up to 75 guests
-- Setup & breakdown included
-
-### Luxury Affair ($3,500)
-- Everything in Premium
-- Premium spirit selection
-- Mixologist consultation
-- 5+ hours of service
-- Unlimited guests
-- Photo booth integration
-
-## Development
-
-### Requirements
-- WordPress 6.0+
-- PHP 8.0+
-- Modern browser support
-
-### Custom Functionality
-- **Quote Forms**: AJAX submission with validation
-- **Package Selection**: Interactive pricing displays
-- **Event Booking**: Custom post type integration
-- **Cocktail Filtering**: Dynamic content filtering
-
-### Building
-The theme is built with modern web standards and requires no build process for basic usage.
-
-### Contributing
-1. Fork the repository
-2. Create a feature branch
-3. Make your changes
-4. Test thoroughly
-5. Submit a pull request
-
-## Support
-
-For support and documentation, visit:
-- [HoustonSipQueen.com](https://houstonsipqueen.com)
-- [Mobile Bartending Resources](https://houstonsipqueen.com/resources)
